    "en": {
      "title": "The amount of rice from the Chinese government to the country today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Chinese embassy said that another consignment of rice provided by the Chinese government to Sri Lanka will arrive in the country today.",
        "An amount of rice provided to Sri Lanka by the Chinese Government was brought to the country on the 25th of last month as rice.",
        "According to the Chinese embassy in Colombo, another rice provided by the Chinese government to Sri Lanka will arrive at the Colombo port today. (a)"
